p.  I haven't worked that hard, or done that much to get as far as I am.  I look at this post in this forum, about epics on Brell.  I see the paladin one is only at 9 while the clerics are somewhere up at 28.  To me, this says that the cleric one is far FAR too easy.  <br>
<br>
As a cleric, I am allowed to say these things, because I can.  If there are 28 epic weapons, and only 9 Paladin ones, even though the paladin ones have been around for MUCH longer, what does that mean?  Only thing I can think of is that either the cleric one is too easy, or the paladin one is too hard.  I don't know, I am just rambling, it bugs me that I should have it easier simply because I am a cleric. <p><CENTER><img src="http://images.honesty.com/imagedata/h/062/62/30626293.jpg"> </CENTER>
